  "original_title": "IMF \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd3 \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF chief happy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "IMF staff and Sri Lankan government officials are very pleased to have reached a staff-level agreement to support the country's economic policies with an Extended Fund Facility of about US$2.9 billion, said Ms. Cristalina George Giova, head of the International Monetary Fund. She said on her Twitter account that this is an important step forward for Sri Lanka."
      ],
